          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1684911217472-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, add the <strong>roasted potatoes & onion</strong> to the <strong>tostadas</strong> and top with the <strong>aguachile-style king prawns</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
